    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Fine-grained powder, typically gunpowder or fulminate, used to ignite the propellant or main explosive in a firearm or explosive device.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
